topic_title: Inconsistent information in the Grading Document and the website

posts.content:
The deadlines mentioned in the Grading Document provided and the TDS website ([s-anand.net](http://s-anand.net)) are different. Project-1’s deadline was 15 Feb, it was then postponed to the 16th of Feb. Can this be reflected here?  
Not affecting me particularly, however, it’s good to be consistent across channels of communication to the students…

images.context: The image is a document outlining the assessment schedule for a "Tools in Data Science" course, which is part of a Diploma program. It details the dates, types, and weightage of various assessments like an online exam (ROE1) and take-home projects (P1 and P2), along with their submission and peer review dates. The document also contains information about eligibility for the final exam and the grading criteria.
